			<h2>Accordian edit form</h2>
			<p>Accordian edit forms limit the user to edit one field at a time. If a user presses a <i>Change</i> button they are presented with the option to edit that field. Other editable fields on the page are disabled until the user saves or cancels the field they are editting.</p>
			<p>Validation appears as shown in the <i>Home phone number</i> field shown below when the <i>Change</i> button is pressed</p>

			<div class="example-box">
			<h6>EXAMPLE ACCORDIAN EDIT FORM</h6>
			<div class="profile-table">
				<div class="row profile-row">
					<div class="col-sm-10 col-xs-8 description-fields">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-sm-4 title-field">Drop-down</div>
							<div class="col-sm-8 uneditable dd-uneditable-div">3</div>
							<div class="col-sm-8 editable dd-editable-div" style="display:none;">
								<select class="uikit-text-input" id="drop-down" name="drop-down">
									<option>-- Select an item --</option>
									<option>Item 1</option>
									<option>Item 2</option>
									<option selected>Item 3</option>
									<option>Item 4</option>
								</select>
								<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary small cancel-dd-button">Cancel</button>
								<button class="uikit-btn small save-dd-button">Save</button>
								<div class="waiting-animation ico-waiting-inline" style="display:none;"></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-4 change-button">
						<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary small edit-dd-button">Change</button>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row profile-row">
					<div class="col-sm-10 col-xs-8 description-fields">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-sm-4 title-field">Input text field</div>
							<div class="col-sm-8 uneditable text-uneditable-div">Input text</div>
							<div class="col-sm-8 editable text-editable-div" style="display:none;">
								<input class="uikit-text-input" name="Input field" id="Input field" type="text" value="Input text" required aria-required="true">
								<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary small cancel-text-button">Cancel</button>
								<button class="uikit-btn small save-text-button">Save</button>
								<div class="waiting-animation ico-waiting-inline" style="display:none;"></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-4 change-button">
						<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary small edit-text-button">Change</button>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row profile-row">
					<div class="col-sm-10 col-xs-8 description-fields">
						<div id="error-example" class="row">
						<div class="col-sm-4 title-field">Home phone number</div>
						<div class="col-sm-8 uneditable home-uneditable-div">
							<span id="home-span" class="no-value">Not provided</span>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-6 editable home-editable-div" style="display:none;">
							<span class="hint display-block">Please include your area code (for example, "03" for Victoria)</span>
							<span id="phone-error" class="input-error-profile" aria-live="polite">Enter a valid home phone number</span>
							<input class="uikit-text-input" name="home-phone" id="home-phone" type="text" value="">
							<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary small cancel-home-button">Cancel</button>
							<button class="uikit-btn small save-home-button">Save</button>
							<div class="waiting-animation ico-waiting-inline" style="display:none;"></div>
						</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-4 change-button">
						<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary small edit-home-button">Change</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
