		<br/>

		<h3>Note on using accordian edit forms</h3>
		<p>The purpose of the accordian edit form is to limit the user to edit one field at a time. Within the form there these limitations exist, however the user is to free to click on navigation items. Clicking on a navigation in the <i>edit</i> state could result in loss of changes. Use a modal in this case to warn the user that they could lose changes.</p>

